headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium this Week: the Canis Freecrawler
content: Swing by the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort and spin the Lucky Wheel to walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery rewards and more. This week's top prize on the podium is none other than the stout, boxy Canis Freecrawler - an off-road vehicle built for the whole family to enjoy.
